In a multicultural Australia full of diversity and continuous change it is important to teach our culture to not only our Aboriginal children but also children from a variety of different backgrounds. However, to a majority of Australian schools credit it is a sad fact that a lot of Aboriginal students are still left behind whether they are taught culture or not. It is for this reason that @blackfitfitness strive to stimulate the Australian curriculum and its outcomes within our programs by TEACHING THROUGH CULTURE rather than solely focusing on teaching culture. Learning and understanding the ways in which Aboriginal & TSI children learn will change the way in which they perceive school, learn & interact with the aspects of a modern western classroom! The facts are there, we learn different. 💭📚✏️⚽️🏈🍃⭐️🍎🍇
